# 5. Another Senior-Level Example (Timing HOF)

```swift
func measureExecutionTime(_ block: () -> Void) {

    let start = CFAbsoluteTimeGetCurrent()

    block()

    let end = CFAbsoluteTimeGetCurrent()

    print("Execution time:", end - start)
}
```

Usage:

```swift
measureExecutionTime {
    for i in 0...100000 {
        print(i)
    }
}
```

