# Key Interview Points

You should mention:

**Higher Order Function characteristics**

• Takes function as parameter
• Returns function
• Uses closures
• Enables functional programming

Examples in Swift:

```
map
filter
reduce
flatMap
compactMap
sorted
forEach
```

